title: Laura-Ingraham-Show-april 1 2016
description:
THE LAURA INGRAHAM SHOW PODCAST April 1, 2016

Guest Host Betsy McCaughey welcomes: Carol Platt Liebau on minimum wage hike "it will cost jobs for small businesses and for people who are struggling to get a foothold on the latter of opportunity" Congressman Steve King on SCOTUS nomination "in the end, our founding fathers set this up to be a political decision" Dr. Sam Clovis "at the convention a lot of those issues sometimes get manipulated" Carl Paladino "the rules committee appointment is probably the most important at the convention"
